originalText.text: Great experience from beginning to end. Dr. Rosen and her staff really care about the patients comfort and safety. All the necessary precautions have been put into place. Everyone on staff was so friendly and nice. The office is very personable and relaxing. Dr. Rosen makes you feel comfortable by explaining everything clearly and performs the procedures painlessly. What I thought was most impressive is that she keeps in touch with you after a visit to make sure you are feeling well and answers any questions.

originalText.text: I have been treated by Dr. Rosen and her expert staff for years and cannot say enough good things about them.  Growing up I dreaded going to the dentist, but I actually look forward to my appointments now. Dr. Rosen and her staff are professional, super friendly, and extremely knowledgeable and skillful.  They are deserving of the highest recommendation.

originalText.text: This is the greatest dentist I have ever been to! Dr. Rosen and her staff are all so personable, kind, patient and skillful. The office manager is always so friendly when I call and come in. The office is clean and relaxing with cool artwork hanging. I live over an hour away now and would never switch. Thank you for your amazing skills! I can’t wait to come back for another cleaning and exam!!!

originalText.text: I've been a patient of Dr. Rosen's for 20 years for one reason: she and her team are PHENOMENAL. I receive high quality care by the most competent, warmest, professional team one could hope for between Dr. Rosen, Laurie and Natalie. They always go out of their way to make me feel comfortable and SAFE, which I especially value during these uncertain times of Covid. I loved Dr. Rosen so much I recommended her to my husband who has also been seeing her for over a decade. I can't say enough positive things about everyone in her office. It's such a pleasure to go in and I look forward to my visits. Highly recommend!
